@NODE "Infos" "Infos"
@TOC "MAIN"

                         5.2 Infos for Programers
                         ************************


The   Tempest  Master  Server  is  written  in  assembler.   There  are  no
System-patches or not allowed programing routines!

TMS didn't need any library.

@ENDNODE

