@NODE "Plans" "Plans"
@TOC "MAIN"
                            6.2 Planed Features
                            *******************
                      
The following features are planed for the TMS or right now available in the
Release-Version:


  o  Diffenrent (background/foreground)-colors in the Node-Window (#1)  for
     different activities:  Ringing, Online, Offline, Chat...aso.  for each
     node.

  o  Amiga.Guide Online-Help with the Help-Key.

  o  Complete new Window-Design (looks great!) (Release Version).
  
  o  Lokale for german and english.

  o  Defineble Gadgets/Buttons.

  o  Hydra-Transfer Display (Upload and Download at the same time!).

  o  Included Stats (Node, Global, User).

  o  Defineble Startup-Modus.

  o  External Preferences-Program.

  o  Local/Sysop-Logon.


  ...do you have any more ideas? Tell us!


@ENDNODE

